<h1>Data Request & Retention Policy</h1>
<p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 11/3/2025<br />
    <strong>Last Updated:</strong> 11/3/2025</p>

<p>This policy outlines how <strong>Flav Creations</strong> (“we”, “us”, or “our”) handles user data requests and manages data retention for <strong>RPGame.Live</strong>.</p>

<h2>1. Data Access and Portability</h2>
<p>You may request access to the personal data we hold about you. Upon verification, we will provide:</p>
<ul>
<li>A summary of collected data (e.g., account info, gameplay history)</li>
<li>Format options for portability (e.g., JSON, CSV)</li>
<li>Estimated delivery time (typically within 30 days)</li>
</ul>
<p>To initiate a request, contact us using the information in Section 5.</p>

<h2>2. Data Correction</h2>
<p>You may request correction of inaccurate or outdated personal data. We will:</p>
<ul>
<li>Verify your identity</li>
<li>Update or annotate the data as appropriate</li>
<li>Confirm completion of the correction</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Data Deletion</h2>
<p>You may request deletion of your personal data. Upon verification, we will:</p>
<ul>
<li>Remove or anonymize data not required for legal, security, or operational purposes</li>
<li>Confirm deletion within a reasonable timeframe</li>
<li>Inform you of any retained data and the reason for retention</li>
</ul>
<p><em>Note:</em> Deletion may affect your ability to access or use the Game.</p>

<h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
<p>We retain personal data only as long as necessary for:</p>
<ul>
<li>Game functionality and user experience</li>
<li>Legal and regulatory compliance</li>
<li>Security, fraud prevention, and abuse monitoring</li>
<li>Backup and recovery operations</li>
</ul>
<p>Retention periods vary by data type. Gameplay logs may be retained longer for analytics and integrity purposes.</p>

<h2>5. Contact and Requests</h2>
<p>To submit a data request, correction, or deletion inquiry, contact:<br />
    📧 <strong>Support@RPGame.Live</strong><br /></p>
<p>Please include:</p>
<ul>
<li>Your username or account ID</li>
<li>The nature of your request</li>
<li>Any relevant supporting documentation</li>
</ul>

<h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this policy to reflect changes in law, technology, or platform operations. Updates will be posted with a revised “Last Updated” date.</p>

<footer>
<p>This Data Request & Retention Policy is part of the legal framework governing your use of <strong>RPGame.Live</strong>.</p>
</footer>
